name: tasty-th
version: 0.1.0
cabal-version: >= 1.6
build-type: Simple
license: BSD3
license-file: BSD3.txt
maintainer: Oscar Finnsson
homepage: http://github.com/bennofs/tasty-th
synopsis: Automagically generate the HUnit- and Quickcheck-bulk-code using Template Haskell.
